      <Properties>
        <Configuration>
          <Text>Author: TAmmy York
Last Update Date: 2026-03-09
Business Purpose:  To monitor and analyze Sagen’s in-force portfolio as of Dec’25, at an anonymized level, at quarterly snapshots (Mar’26, Jun’26, Sep’26, Dec’26), to determine portfolio trends based on updated credit bureau information.</Text>
